{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, these models are versatile and have been successfully applied across different domains, including medical imaging, autonomous driving, and agricultural monitoring, showcasing their wide-ranging applicability (Upadhyay et al. 2024).",
    "However, there are notable limitations to these models.",
    "One significant challenge is their dependency on large amounts of labeled data for training.",
    "Without sufficient annotated datasets, the performance of these models can be limited.",
    "In comparison, advanced models often incorporate unsupervised or semi-supervised learning techniques to mitigate this dependency."
  ]
}